        <h3 class="auto-style1">
          &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  <span class="auto-style1">Welcome to the Central Library which is one of the central support services of ICE. The mission of the Central Library is to provide information services and access to bibliographic and full text digital and printed resources to support the scholarly and informational needs of the Institute Community</span>.
        </h3></div>
        <p class="auto-style1">
